　are ranked according to their
　Cumulative Score, and eligible to

　Tap the [Rewards] button for more
　information.

■Dungeon Rules
・You can try the Dungeon as many
　times as you like.

・No Continues allowed.

・Enemies do not attack.

・Erase a certain amount of
　designated Orbs before the
　timer runs out to clear.

・You can replenish some 
　time by matching Heal Orbs.

・The game starts with all monsters'
　skills maxed up but you can use
　them only 1 time for each monster.

・The dungeon levels up each time
　you erase a certain amount of
　Orbs. With each level-up, the timer
　will fully replenish but will
　be decreasing faster.
　Furthermore, the higher the dungeon
　level is, the higher your score for
　each combo will be.

・Your score is calculated by the
　the number of combos you make
　and Orbs you erase each time.

・The maximum Cumulative Score
　is 999,999.

・After entering the dungeon, if the
　device is put into sleep mode, or
　if you change to another app even
　once, the timer will still be
　decreasing, and your score will
　not be registered in the ranking.

・If you restart the app after
　entering the dungeon, you will
　leave the dungeon and will not be
　participating in the ranking.

Tap the [Rules] button for more
